WEBVTT

00:01:29.360 --> 00:01:31.736
If there were any
seven-year-olds in the audience,

00:01:31.760 --> 00:01:34.256
they'd be like, "Yes!"

00:01:34.280 --> 00:01:37.120
So what about if you had
a machine that could do it for you?

00:01:42.800 --> 00:01:45.920
(Laughter)

00:01:46.720 --> 00:01:47.960
I call it ...

00:01:50.360 --> 00:01:52.320
I call it "The Toothbrush Helmet."

00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:55.680
(Laughter)

00:01:57.480 --> 00:02:00.216
(Robot arm buzzing)